LINK: https://www.namastesql.com/coding-problem/38-product-reviews?question_type=0&level_id=82791DA7C5D439BA

==> My approach:
SELECT * 
FROM product_reviews
WHERE (
    LOWER(review_text) COLLATE SQL_Latin1_General_CP1_CI_AS LIKE '%excellent%' 
    OR LOWER(review_text) COLLATE SQL_Latin1_General_CP1_CI_AS LIKE '%amazing%'
    )
      AND LOWER(review_text) NOT LIKE '%not excellent%'
      AND LOWER(review_text) NOT LIKE '%not amazing%';
